{"tid":2279837,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大三罷兩青年被控非法集結及蒙面 事隔一年今首度提堂","createTime":"2020-11-10T05:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T06:32:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d2cbc24752672ef7d164f75240a638f8e39f0274","tid":2279837,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T05:19:19.000Z","msg":"去年11月「大三罷」期間，大批市民被捕。有學生和兼職侍應在西灣河港鐵站附近被指參與非法集結及使用蒙面物品，因而被捕，事隔一年遭落案起訴，今於東區裁判法院提堂。兩人暫時毋須答辯，案件押後至明年1月8日再訊，以待辯方索取法律意見，其間兩人獲准各以2,000元保釋候訊。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官應辯方申請，押後案件以待辯方索取文件及法律意見。兩被告保釋期間，須每周向警署報到一次。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，首被告警誡下自言只是八卦而到現場拍照，戴口罩則因當時有點咳嗽，亦為保障私隱。次被告則自言在附近工作，因而路經該處。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201110/KSOXB7RWKFCENJDHPUBPQTM4OE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201110%2FKSOXB7RWKFCENJDHPUBPQTM4OE%2F&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y4cyEe9XGSmm9RGcz8BbYLg%3D&h=16a759ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201110%2FKSOXB7RWKFCENJDHPUBPQTM4OE%2F&h=b4432c4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201110/KSOXB7RWKFCENJDHPUBPQTM4OE/</a>"},{"pid":"f161c7bf95e91aba5f4f033447abadca90d3453f","tid":2279837,"uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T05:44:25.000Z","msg":"兩人被控一項非法集結罪，指他們於去年 11 月 13 日，在香港西灣河港鐵站 B 出口外和其他不知名人士，參與憑藉《公安條例》第 18 ( 1 ) 條屬非法集結的集結。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%89%E7%BD%B7-%E5%85%A9%E7%94%B7%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90-%E4%BA%8B%E9%9A%94%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7-%E7%8D%B2%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E5%80%99%E8%A8%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25B8%2589%25E7%25BD%25B7-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590-%25E4%25BA%258B%25E9%259A%2594%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2